#

Apple Crumble Pie

60 min
$10
300 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

glutendairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Dessert

Tags:

desserteasycomfort food

Description

Warm, sweet apples under a crunchy crumble topping, perfect for dessert!

Ingredients

  • apples: 6 cups, peeled and sliced
  • sugar: 1/2 cup
  • cinnamon: 1 tsp
  • lemon juice: 1 tbsp
  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • rolled oats: 1/2 cup
  • brown sugar: 1/2 cup
  • butter: 1/2 cup, melted
  • pie crust: 1, store-bought
